title: EVARU
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Vasco The Rebel
subTitle: With unwavering support from his lover, a defiant young man carves his way into the mafia world. His journey takes a turn when a relentless police officer pursues him.

title: Bal Ganesh 3
subTitle: Dhoti, Topi and Suit Boot are more than happy to oblige when a group of alien kids come over to listen to adventure stories about their favourite Bal Ganesh.

title: Thadam
subTitle: While investigating the death of a man, the police track down their lead suspect. However, the case takes a twisted turn when they discover a clone of their suspect.

title: Aavesham
subTitle: Three boys move into a hostel to pursue engineering, where they clash with seniors. To get revenge, they befriend a gangster.

title: Garam
subTitle: Varala, a jobless young man, leaves his home to prove himself to his father. However, before achieving his goal, he falls in love with Sameera and tries to woo and save her from gangster Biju.

title: Power Unlimited 2
subTitle: Karthikeya, a man who is devoted to his family, faces a huge challenge as his violent and turbulent past begins to resurface.

title: Yashoda
subTitle: Surrogate mother Yashodha is advised to follow a few guidelines to keep herself and her baby healthy and safe. However, something happens at the surrogate centre that puts both of them at risk.

title: Dashing CM Bharath
subTitle: Oxford graduate Bharat assumes his late father's role as chief minister. He strives to reform a corrupt society, but encounters fierce opposition from adversaries.

title: Geethanjali Malli Vachindi
subTitle: Sreenu receives a directorial offer from Vishnu to shoot in a bungalow. Later, him and his crew realise that Vishnu orchestrated the ploy to seek revenge by trapping them in a haunted house.

title: Geethanjali Malli Vachindi
subTitle: Sreenu receives a directorial offer from Vishnu to shoot in a bungalow. Later, him and his crew realise that Vishnu orchestrated the ploy to seek revenge by trapping them in a haunted house.

title: Ghatak Returns
subTitle: Gauthan, uninterested in romance, slowly finds his world shifting when Sandhya enters his life, but before he understands his feelings, family decisions complicate matters.

title: Khakee
subTitle: A deputy commissioner and his crew attempt to transport a terrorist to Mumbai, but their mission is thwarted by an ex-policeman with an agenda of his own.

title: Rowdy Baadshah
subTitle: A man fails to get a job with the police force due to his father's connections with a gangster. However, when his brother is killed by the latter, he sets out on the path of revenge.

title: Anjaniputra
subTitle: A businessman saves a policeman from a group of thugs. As a result, he incurs the wrath of a ruthless local gangster who is also an assassin.

title: Sangharsh Aur Vijay
subTitle: Badri is the protector of Badrinath temple. However, when a woman falls in love with him, his guru decides against making Badri his successor.

title: Main Hoon Dandadhikari
subTitle: Following his father's death, a man gives up on his dream to become a film-maker and joins the police force. He then attempts to track down a psychopathic killer who targets schoolgirls.

title: Darbar
subTitle: Aaditya, a high-ranking law enforcement official, sets out to eradicate the city's gangsters. As the events unfold, it becomes clear that his motivations are deeply personal.

title: Surya's Saturday
subTitle: A vigilante fights against injustice using his own unique moral code, where he only comes out to play on Saturdays.

title: Seetharamam
subTitle: Afreen, a Pakistani woman, heads to India in order to deliver a love letter written in 1965 to fulfill her grandfather's dying wish. However, the journey alters her life forever.

title: Seetharamam

title: Ezra
subTitle: After Priya buys an antique box, she and Ranjan experience eerie events. Later, they seek a rabbi's help to uncover its dark history and confront the malevolent force within.

title: Vardi Ki Aan
subTitle: An upright police officer vows to punish the culprits involved in the brutal rape of a young woman. However, his investigations unravel a shocking secret about his own father's despicable crimes.

title: Ek Tha Nayak
subTitle: When a respected police officer is killed by a gangster, his younger brother decides to avenge him by hunting the man down.

title: International Khiladi: The Iron Man
subTitle: Amrita's parents get killed. Years later, she falls in love with Aditya only to learn that he was the one who was accused of her parents' murder.

title: Dumdaar Khiladi
subTitle: A man and a woman develop a great bond after the latter arrives in Hyderabad. However, they realise their love for each other when the woman's marriage is arranged to a person of her parent's choice.

title: Kadamban
subTitle: Kadamban lives a peaceful life with the villagers in a remote forest in Tamil Nadu. Things take a turn when a business tycoon decides to drive his tribe out of the area in order to extract minerals.

title: Roberrt
subTitle: Raghava, the head cook in a catering unit, leads a peaceful life with his son Arjun. However, their bliss is short-lived as Raghava's past comes back to haunt him.

title: Vivegam
subTitle: Ajay Kumar, a former counter-terrorism agent, is called for a special mission. However, he is betrayed by his friends and is accused of extremely treasonous acts.

title: Ek Hi Maqsad
subTitle: Captain Ram is a military commando who rescues Patil, the tourism minister of Karnataka from Jehadi terrorists. Taking a liking for his heroics, Patil engages him to provide security.
